title: 32/1/17 A and 17/9/17 S+
body: I did a match and I did use Veigar. I did 32/1/17 and I taked A, my friend did 17/9/17 and he taked S+. How does it be possible???? A bug switched our valutation???

replies.body: Dipende dalla farm. Se avevi (per esempio) in 40 minuti 80 di farm te lo puoi anche scordare. No farm=no S.

Hi, this is the italian forum!
Is kinda weird that a bug can make possible that situation, you probably dont deserve that S+ for your farm, damage, ward...
